I"<h4 id="官网"><a href="https://cocoapods.org/">官网</a></h4>
<ul>
  <li>Swift 和 Objective-C Cocoa 项目的包管理工具</li>
  <li>iOS 开发的必备工具</li>
</ul>

<h4 id="安装">安装</h4>
<ol>
  <li>CocoaPods 是用 Ruby 构建的,可以用 macOS 上的默认 Ruby 进行安装</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo gem install cocoapods</code></li>
</ol>

<p>⚠️ ERROR: While executing gem … (Gem::FilePermissionError).
	You don’t have write permissions for the /usr/bin directory.</p>
<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo gem install -n /usr/local/bin fastlane</code></li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo gem install -n /usr/local/bin cocoapods</code></li>
</ul>

<h4 id="管理依赖">管理依赖</h4>
<ul>
  <li>创建 Podfile 文件（XXXX.xcodeproj 所在文件夹）</li>
  <li>Podfile内容：</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>platform :ios, '8.0'
use_frameworks!

target 'Target Name' do
  pod 'AFNetworking', '~&gt; 2.6'
  pod 'ORStackView', '~&gt; 3.0'
  pod 'SwiftyJSON', '~&gt; 2.3'
end
</code></pre></div></div>
<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pod init</code></li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pod install</code></li>
</ul>

<h4 id="创建cocoapods包">创建CocoaPods包</h4>
<ul>
  <li>```
pod spec create LouisProject
edit Peanut.podspec
pod spec lint Peanut.podspec</li>
</ul>

<p>```</p>

